featureScore([F-W2|L],ID,S1-S3):- feature(ID,F,W1), S2 is S1+(W1*W2), featureScore(L,ID,S2-S3).
score([_:_:Anaphor],Antecedent,Proximity,Score):- ana_id(Anaphor,ID), extractFeatures(Antecedent,Features,0,Len), W is 1/Len, featureScore([(prox:Proximity)-W|Features],ID,0-Score).
